### F3008-220001 - Press-Brake Shear ACAN

The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) is announcing the availability of a contract for the procurement of one Press-Brake Shear machine tool as outlined in the Advance Contract Award Notice (ACAN) document F3008-220001.

#### Contract Details

*   Contract Reference Number: WS3779411298
*   Solicitation Number: WS3779411298
*   Publication Date: December 8, 2022
*   Tender Closing Date: December 23, 2022 at 2:00 pm EST
*   Expected Contract Start Date: None
*   Expected Contract End Date: None

#### Contract Description

The client is the Department of Fisheries and Oceans Canada, and the requirement is for a single Press-Brake Shear machine tool. The proposed machine tool must be delivered to Sorel, Quebec as soon as possible after contract award.

#### Contract Documents and Amendments

*   The Advance Contract Award Notice (ACAN) document F3008-220001 contains all the required information and instructions for the contract award.
*   All required ACAN documents must be submitted by the tender closing date at 2:00 pm EST. Any documents received after this time may be refused.

#### Handing of Contract Documents

It is the responsibility of the contractor to ensure that all documents are properly formatted and submitted on time. Late or incomplete submissions may result in rejection of the bid.

#### Contact Information

Questions or concerns regarding the tender and contract award process can be directed to:
*   Delgado Garcia, Oscar (SPAC/PSPC)
*   email: [oscar.delgadogarcia@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:oscar.delgadogarcia@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)
*   phone: None
*   fax: None
*   URL: [http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14838644?extsite=MTQ4Mzg2NDRfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14838644?extsite=MTQ4Mzg2NDRfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==)
